Trans-Fictitious Game

	Philosophy

		-
			A trans-fictitious game, or TFG, is any augmented-reality game that results in
			real-life consequences that transcend the scope of the game itself.
		-

	Principles

		Realm Compendiums

			-
				Realm compendiums may be used to give structure and context to TFGs, and realm
				sagas may be constructed from said compendiums to guide gameplay.
